flowchart TB
    A[Human / Organization Decision] --> B[Agent Execution Envelope]
    B --> B1[Agent identity]
    B --> B2[Owner role]
    B --> B3[Authority scope]
    B --> B4[Tool scope]
    B --> B5[Data access scope]
    B --> B6[Human review gate]
    B --> B7[Audit log]
    B --> B8[Rollback path]
    B --> B9[Stop condition]
    B --> C[AI Agent Action]
    C --> D{Post-check}
    D -->|pass| E[Commit / Execute]
    D -->|fail| F[Hold / Rollback / Escalate]
